---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Ladies Night Pottery Painting"
  description="Girls' night out pottery painting and creative bonding in Centerville, TN. Perfect for ladies looking for a fun evening together."
  price="$20-30 per person"
  duration="1.5-2 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="ladies night pottery, girls night out, women's pottery painting, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h2>Ladies Night Pottery Painting - Centerville, TN</h2>
    <p>Gather your girlfriends for a creative ladies' night out! Paint pottery, share laughs, and bond over a fun, relaxing evening. This is the perfect girls' night activity—creative, social, and absolutely memorable.</p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>This is pottery painting designed for women to connect and create together. You'll choose from a wide selection of pottery pieces, paint in a welcoming atmosphere, and enjoy quality time with your favorite ladies. Whether it's your regular girls' night crew or a special celebration, this experience is all about bonding and creativity.</p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Selection of pottery pieces perfect for ladies</li>
      <li>All painting supplies, brushes, and paints</li>
      <li>Expert guidance and creative inspiration</li>
      <li>Professional glazing and kiln-firing</li>
      <li>Welcoming, ladies-focused atmosphere</li>
      <li>Take-home your finished piece</li>
      <li>Option: Café refreshments available</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Regular girls' night groups</li>
      <li>Birthday celebrations with the ladies</li>
      <li>Bachelorette party activities</li>
      <li>Women's groups and clubs</li>
      <li>Mother-daughter bonding time</li>
      <li>Any group of ladies seeking fun and creativity</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Welcome and introductions (5 minutes)</li>
      <li>Browse and select your pottery piece (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Paint, chat, and create together (60-75 minutes)</li>
      <li>Finishing touches and group photos (15 minutes)</li>
      <li>Take home your beautiful creation</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $20-30 per person<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 1.5-2 hours<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> All levels welcome—no experience needed
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Book your ladies' night pottery painting!</strong> Call (931) 729-8459 or email made@thelocalplacetn.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Best girls' night ever! We laughed so much and everyone loved painting together. Already planning our next visit!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Rachel & Friends</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Perfect for my birthday celebration with my girlfriends. The atmosphere was so welcoming and we had an amazing time!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Lauren</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
